<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>내 정보 수정 - ESS-M.S</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/1.main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/6.signup.css"> 
    <style>
        .edit-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .edit-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .save-btn {
            flex: 2;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cancel-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo" onclick="location.href='1.main.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">ESS-M.S</h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="edit-container">
        <div class="edit-header">
            <h2>회원 정보 수정</h2>
            <p>변경하실 정보를 입력해 주세요.</p>
        </div>

        <form id="editForm">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>이름</label>
                <input type="text" id="editName" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" required>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>이메일</label>
                <input type="email" id="editEmail" placeholder="example@mail.com">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>연락처</label>
                <input type="tel" id="editPhone" placeholder="010-0000-0000">
            </div>

            <div class="btn-group">
                <button type="submit" class="save-btn">변경사항 저장</button>
                <a href="11.mypage.html" class="cancel-btn">취소</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <script src="js/12.edit_profile.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
